.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"image,4106,200,CRW_3673.JPG\" alt=\"\" /><img style=\"float: right;\" src=\"image,4106,200,CRW_3679.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></p>',NULL,4106,5,1,NULL,17);
INSERT INTO `publications_publication` VALUES
(3032,'P','2011-12-18',0,NULL,'Note','VIII ФЕСТИВАЛЬ-КОНКУРС ДУХОВНОЇ ПІСНІ «АСКОЛЬДІВ ГЛАС» у світлинах','<p><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"image,4107,200,CRW_3200.JPG\" alt=\"\" /><img style=\"float: right;\" src=\"image,4107,200,CRW_3227.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></p>','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">Фото Любові Михайлюк</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"image,4107,200,CRW_3111.JPG\" alt=\"\" /><img style=\"float: right;\" src=\"image,4107,200,CRW_3105.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"image,4107,200,CRW_3119.JPG\" alt=\"\" /><img style=\"float: right;\" src=\"image,4107,200,CRW_3127.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"image,4107,200,CRW_3136.JPG\" alt=\"\" /><img style=\"float: right;\" src=\"image,4107,200,CRW_3129.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></span></span></p>\r\