\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #111111; font-weight: normal;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://podrobnosti.ua/criminal/2011/06/14/775147.html\" target=\"_blank\">http<span lang=\"RU\">://</span>podrobnosti<span lang=\"RU\">.</span>ua<span lang=\"RU\">/</span>criminal<span lang=\"RU\">/2011/06/14/775147.</span>html</a></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; vertical-align: top;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #111111; font-weight: normal;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://ura-inform.com/ru/neformat/2011/06/14/vandals\" target=\"_blank\">http<span lang=\"RU\">://</span>ura<span lang=\"RU\">-</span>inform<span lang=\"RU\">.</span>com<span lang=\"RU\">/</span>ru<span lang=\"RU\">/</span>neformat<span lang=\"RU\">/2011/06/14/</span>vandals</a></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; vertical-align: top;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #111111; font-weight: normal;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.aif.ua/society/news/36616\" target=\"_blank\">http<span lang=\"RU\">://</span>www<span lang=\"RU\">.</span>aif<span lang=\"RU\">.</span>ua<span lang=\"RU\">/</span>society<span lang=\"RU\">/</span>news<span lang=\"RU\">/36616</span></a></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; vertical-align: top;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #111111; font-weight: normal;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://gazetavv.com/analytics/crime/21007-vandaly-spilili-krest-pod-askoldovoy-mogiloy.html\" target=\"_blank\">http<span lang=\"RU\">://</span>gazetavv<span lang=\"RU\">.</span>com<span lang=\"RU\">/</span>analytics<span lang=\"RU\">/</span>crime<span lang=\"RU\">/21007-</span>vandaly<span lang=\"RU\">-</span>